Body: Description: Is Google Authenticator the only 2FA app supported? What about Microsoft Authenticator or a third-party like DUO?

What We've Learned Updated: The 2FA mechanism implemented in EPP relies on the standard format for Time-Based One-Time Password (TOTP) systems.

The generated QR code is compatible with any mobile app that supports TOTP-based two-factor authentication.
Next Steps Updated: Waiting on customer to confirm we can close this ticket.
